MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

93-2510. R & L Transfer, Inc. v. Tracy.

Board of Tax Appeals, No. 91-A-1539. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Board of Tax Appeals. Upon consideration of appellant’s application to dismiss,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that said application be, and the same is hereby, granted, effective • January 6, 1994.
